    <a title="Amber Anderson" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1411768-amber-anderson"><img alt="Amber Anderson" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1335225706p2/1411768.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
