    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1749077541" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2441410401481060284">I loved this story of a late 19th century woman who maintained a joi de vive and love of beauty despite life’s toils and hardships. The characterizations in this novel was amazing. Ferber made these characters pulse with life. This is my first book by Ferber and I want to read much more.</span>

